# Tetris (Unity + C#)

Classic Tetris implementation built in Unity with grid-based logic.

---

## Gameplay Overview

Players control falling tetromino pieces and clear full lines to gain score.

---

## Features

- Grid-based movement system
- Piece rotation system
- Line clearing algorithm
- Score system
- Game over detection

---

## Technical Highlights

- 2D grid data structure
- Collision detection system
- Rotation logic for tetromino pieces
- Game state management

